high_descs: Turn around and go to the desk in the bedroom.
Take the butterknife from the table.
Turn around and go near the eggplant on the kitchen table.
Cut the eggplant into pieces using the knife.
Turn around and go near the coffeetable in the living room.
Put the butterknife on the coffeetable.
Turn around and go near the eggplant on the kitchen table.
Take the eggplant from the table.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the eggplant into the refrigerator and cooled it.
Then take it out and go near the coffeetable in the living room.
Put the eggplant on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the knife and piece of Eggplant on the CoffeeTable in the living room.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the desk.
Pick up butter knife from the desk.
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the counter top.
slice egg plant on the counter top.
Turn around and walk to the coffee table to your left.
Place butter knife on the coffee table.
Head straight towards the counter top by turning around and turning left.
Pick up egg plant  from the counter top
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the fridge.
Place egg plant on the fridge
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near coffee table
Place egg egg plant on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Slicing egg plant and cooling it, placing it on fridge

high_descs: Turn around, go left to enter a tiny room, turn right and leave, immediately turn left, follow the wall on your left until there's an entrance there, go inside and get to the desk.
Pick up a butterknife from the upper part of the table.
Leave the eggplant and immediately turn left and go to the microwave.
Cut the eggplant next to the microwave using the knife.
Turn right, walk alongside the adjacent wall, go left when you see an entrance to a room right to your left, go towards it but do not enter, instead turn right and walk to the coffeetable.
Place the butterknife on the coffeetable.
Now head to the opposite corner of the room, and get to the eggplant.
Pick up the eggplant slice from next to the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the other side.
Put the eggplant slice inside the fridge, let it cool there, and take it out.
Go back to the coffeetable where you left the knife.
Put the eggplant slice on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled eggplant slice on the coffee table.
